        <div style="margin: 40px 0;">
            <h2 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;">What is a Cataract?</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">A cataract is the clouding of the natural lens in your eye, which leads to a decrease in vision. It is a common age-related condition that can affect one or both eyes. Cataracts typically develop gradually and can significantly impact your quality of life if left untreated.</p>
            
            <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: #8b0000; margin-bottom: 15px;">Common Symptoms</h3>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="color: #8b0000; font-size: 8px;"></i>
                        <span>Blurred or cloudy vision</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="color: #8b0000; font-size: 8px;"></i>
                        <span>Difficulty seeing at night</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="color: #8b0000; font-size: 8px;"></i>
                        <span>Sensitivity to light and glare</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="color: #8b0000; font-size: 8px;"></i>
                        <span>Seeing 'halos' around lights</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="color: #8b0000; font-size: 8px;"></i>
                        <span>Fading or yellowing of colors</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin: 40px 0;">
            <h2 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;">The Surgery Process</h2>
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;">
                <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #8b0000; margin-bottom: 15px;">Before Surgery</h3>
                    <p>A comprehensive eye examination will be performed to evaluate your eye health and determine the most suitable treatment plan. We will discuss your options for intraocular lens implants and address any concerns you may have.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #8b0000; margin-bottom: 15px;">During Surgery</h3>
                    <p>The procedure typically takes 20-30 minutes and is performed under local anaesthetic. Using advanced microsurgical techniques, the cloudy lens is removed and replaced with a custom-selected artificial lens.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #8b0000; margin-bottom: 15px;">After Surgery</h3>
                    <p>Most patients notice improved vision within a few days. Full recovery typically takes 4-6 weeks. You'll receive detailed aftercare instructions and scheduled follow-up appointments to monitor your progress.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

